1) cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with small object tracking, which is a subfield of computer vision. 
2) cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a new descriptor based on saliency, which is a common technique in AI. 
3) cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper may involve machine learning techniques for feature extraction and classification. 
4) cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with visual tracking, which is a multimedia application. 
5) cs.RO (Robotics) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper may have implications for robotic vision and tracking.
